{"word":"G1839 - ἐξίστημι - exístēmi - ex-is'-tay-mee - Amaze","slug":"G1839","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐξίστημι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>exístēmi"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ex-is'-tay-mee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Amaze"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B5;&#x0313;&#x03BE;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03C3;&#x03C4;&#x03B7;&#x03BC;&#x03B9; - existe&#x0304;mi</b> - <i>ex-is'-tay-mee</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G1537\">G1537</a> and <a href=\"#/G2476\">G2476</a>; to <i>put</i> (<i>stand</i>) <i>out</i> of wits, that is, <i>astound</i>, or (reflexively) <i>become astounded</i>, <i>insane:</i> - amaze, be (make) astonished, be beside self (selves), bewitch, wonder."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1611\">G1611</a>"}]}